Wordle 240 3/6

⬛⬛⬛⬛⬛ &gt;!ABOUT!&lt;

⬛🟨🟩⬛⬛ &gt;!MINES!&lt;

🟩🟩🟩🟩🟩 &gt;!CYNIC!&lt;

Been forever since I got a three turn. I always start with those first two words as it gives me all five vowels as well as some big letters &gt;!(MNTS)!&lt;. Seeing I had the &gt;!N in the right spot and only an I!&lt; had me stumped at first but I worked through the word and letter patterns I knew. I couldn’t think of a word that started with &gt;!I and had four non vowels after it, even favoring in Y!&lt; so I knew it had to be the fourth or fifth letter. Again I couldn’t think of a word where it’s &gt;!three constants and an I so Y has to be in it and it would make the most sense to be YNI or YN_I!&lt; so let’s type that in, with X as a placeholder, and see if anything clicks. Now go through the alphabet. &gt;!C makes CYNIC!&lt; All green, here we go.,9,3,"['about', 'mines', 'cynic']",cynic,6

