&gt;!That was a hard one! Took me a while, on that fourth guess at first I was trying to think of something that would fit with 'OOL' at the end, then when going for the 'OLL' I couldn't get 'DROLL' out of my head for a while.!&lt;,8,4,"['equal', 'idiot', 'whorl', 'knoll']",knoll,14

I never go with a mathematically recommended starting guess like &gt;!crane!&lt; but I did today and it really paid off. That gave me two green letters immediately and then it was just a a matter of making solid guesses.

